=== training DONE. dev AUROC/AUPRC in experiments/refsingle_ENC-002_CTCF_ctcf_ref_single_classification_binsplit2/runs/clf/train.log ===
    COMPARE dev AUROC/AUPRC to the ref_alt_pair binsplit2 run (AUROC 0.672 / AUPRC 0.130):
      ref_single >= pair  => the ref/alt contrast is NOT adding signal (single window suffices)
      ref_single <  pair  => the twin contrast contributes real allelic signal
    Both runs use the SAME bin-split + train-only balance, so the delta is the representation.
